{"contents":[{"text":"in my second dream, i was basically reciting my first dream today to friends. that's crazy.

"},{"text":"first dream was: me and ammar share same room which also has a common area. ammar had to help one if the f&b shop in preparing burgers. i offered to help. that guy gave it all to me and that aunty who owned the shop to do and went back saying he had some other work. aunty was teaching me how to make burgers. then i started making more faster. i noticed burning smell. in a corner, an induction was on and plastic kept beside it which was touching the surface was burning i immediately turned it off from the switchboard but yk how it sometimes is still on? i couldn't switch it off from the power buttons. whenever i did it'd just change heat settings. So I told the aunty and we ran out. Running out thru hostel corridor I yelled fire fire in 113. i wondered what if my room burns down. i cant lose my laptop and ipad. so i after 5 mins, ran back in and saw two guards trying to extinguish fire from the wiring. i took my laptop, ipad and phone and ran out. and then in second? (maybe first only) i was telling this story to my friends. 

